# Issue 002: Setup Development Environment

## Current Behavior
No development environment configured for C++ compilation and City of Heroes server development.

## Intended Behavior
Fully configured development environment with all necessary tools, compilers, and dependencies for building and modifying the City of Heroes server.

## Suggested Implementation Steps
1. Identify required C++ compiler version and tools
2. Install build system dependencies (make, cmake, etc.)
3. Set up version control (git configuration)
4. Install database development libraries
5. Configure IDE or text editor for C++ development
6. Test compilation environment with a simple C++ project
7. Document the environment setup process

